Class SchedulersTransformer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appliedrec.rxverid.SchedulersTransformer<T>
  • Type Parameters:

    io.reactivex.CompletableTransformer, io.reactivex.FlowableTransformer<T,T>, io.reactivex.MaybeTransformer<T,T>, io.reactivex.ObservableTransformer<T,T>, io.reactivex.SingleTransformer<T,T>

    public class SchedulersTransformer<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements io.reactivex.ObservableTransformer<T,T>, io.reactivex.SingleTransformer<T,T>, io.reactivex.FlowableTransformer<T,T>, io.reactivex.MaybeTransformer<T,T>, io.reactivex.CompletableTransformer
    Transformer that can be used in a Observable.compose(ObservableTransformer), Single.compose(SingleTransformer), Maybe.compose(MaybeTransformer), Completable.compose(CompletableTransformer) and Flowable.compose(FlowableTransformer) to subscribe and observe on specified schedulers
    Since:
    1.10.0
